graph TD
    User((User/Creator)) -->|Upload/Request| API[API Gateway - NestJS]
    API -->|Auth/Meta| DB[(PostgreSQL)]
    API -->|Store| S3[S3 Source Bucket]
    
    S3 -->|Event| Orchestrator[Workflow Orchestrator - Temporal.io]
    
    Orchestrator -->|Dispatch| Queue{Message Broker - RabbitMQ}
    
    subgraph "AI Worker Cluster (GPU/CPU)"
        Worker1[Audio Worker: Whisper]
        Worker2[Visual Worker: YOLO/SAM]
        Worker3[Text Worker: LLM]
    end
    
    Queue --> Worker1
    Queue --> Worker2
    Queue --> Worker3
    
    Worker1 & Worker2 & Worker3 -->|Metadata| Redis[(Redis State)]
    
    Redis --> Assembly[Assembly Worker: FFmpeg/Editly]
    Assembly -->|Final Export| S3_Out[S3 Optimized Bucket]
    S3_Out --> API
    API -->|Notify| User